description: Love and Drugs on the Street: Girls Sleeping Rough Sociopolitical Documentary hosted by Lily Murray, published by BBC in 2017 - English narration http://docuwiki.net/images/e/e0/Love-and-Drugs-on-the-Street-Girls-Sleeping-Rough-Cover.jpg Information ------------------------------ Love and Drugs on the Street: Girls Sleeping Rough Eye-opening stories of the daily lives of women sleeping rough on Brighton's streets. 3) Break Up The eye-opening daily life story of women sleeping rough on Brighton's streets continues.
